-Pass the ball to me!
-[boy 3] Yeah! Come on!

00:00:39.908 --> 00:00:40.875 position:41% line:83% align:start
[boy 3]
Whoa!

00:00:40.909 --> 00:00:42.075 position:41% line:83% align:start
[boy 1]
Taro!

