-Give me the ball!
-Hey, give it back!

00:00:45.013 --> 00:00:46.748 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:00:46.781 --> 00:00:48.750 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:00:48.783 --> 00:00:51.385 position:13% line:83% align:start
-[boy 3]Hey! Pass it over!
-[boy 2] Nice one, Taro!

00:00:51.418 --> 00:00:53.888 position:19% line:83% align:start
