-Finished.
-[boy 3] [laugh]

00:00:54.989 --> 00:00:56.056 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[boy 3] Yeah!

00:00:56.089 --> 00:00:57.792 position:24% line:83% align:start
