00:01:02.062 --> 00:01:02.997 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mm-hm.

00:01:03.031 --> 00:01:05.098 position:13% line:89% align:start
Are you really going away?

00:01:05.132 --> 00:01:07.334 position:10% line:83% align:start
