you've transferred here.

00:01:07.367 --> 00:01:09.436 position:10% line:89% align:start
Can't you at least stay here

00:01:09.469 --> 00:01:11.338 position:30% line:83% align:start
until the next
school tournament?

00:01:11.371 --> 00:01:14.308 position:19% line:83% align:start
[boy 2] We'd be sure to
win it if you were here.

00:01:14.341 --> 00:01:15.944 position:19% line:89% align:start
No, I can't stay here.

00:01:15.977 --> 00:01:17.779 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's about my father's work.

00:01:17.812 --> 00:01:19.479 position:41% line:83% align:start
[boy 1]
Oh, come on!

00:01:19.514 --> 00:01:20.515 position:44% line:89% align:start
Taro!

00:01:21.916 --> 00:01:24.184 position:30% line:83% align:start
Well, everyone.
Take care now!

00:01:24.217 --> 00:01:25.553 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Aww!

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:27.722 position:19% line:83% align:start
-See you soon, Tarooo!
-Bye!

00:01:27.755 --> 00:01:29.857 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Come back soon!
-Bye!

00:01:29.891 --> 00:01:31.693 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh, poor Taro...

00:01:31.726 --> 00:01:33.427 position:13% line:89% align:start
I really feel bad for him.

00:01:33.460 --> 00:01:35.295 position:27% line:83% align:start
I understand that
his father is a painter

00:01:35.329 --> 00:01:37.197 position:24% line:83% align:start
who travels around
the country.

00:01:37.230 --> 00:01:38.465 position:21% line:83% align:start
[boy 1] But he had to
transfer schools

00:01:38.498 --> 00:01:41.569 position:24% line:83% align:start
over 30 times just
in elementary school.

00:01:41.603 --> 00:01:44.572 position:19% line:83% align:start
If that's how it goes,
he won't ever make friends.

