If you can't even take
this ball away from me,

00:03:41.488 --> 00:03:42.657 position:19% line:89% align:start
You can't even dream of

00:03:42.690 --> 00:03:44.859 position:16% line:83% align:start
winning against Shutetsu
at the tournament.

00:03:44.892 --> 00:03:47.461 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:03:47.494 --> 00:03:48.730 position:44% line:89% align:start
Oh...

00:03:48.763 --> 00:03:51.165 position:38% line:83% align:start
[laughs]
What happened?

00:03:51.199 --> 00:03:52.600 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:03:52.633 --> 00:03:54.068 position:38% line:83% align:start
