Come on, let's go again!

00:03:54.102 --> 00:03:55.302 position:44% line:89% align:start
Okay!

00:03:55.636 --> 00:03:56.403 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:03:57.004 --> 00:03:57.972 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunts]
-Oh! Whoa!

00:03:58.005 --> 00:04:02.677 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:04:07.582 --> 00:04:10.151 position:21% line:83% align:start
[grunt] Oh, hi, Mom!
I'm back!

00:04:10.184 --> 00:04:11.451 position:24% line:89% align:start
Welcome back, son.

00:04:11.485 --> 00:04:12.920 position:24% line:89% align:start
Breakfast is ready.

00:04:12.954 --> 00:04:15.790 position:41% line:83% align:start
[pant]
Thanks!

00:04:15.823 --> 00:04:17.290 position:21% line:89% align:start
'Morning, Mrs. Ozora.

00:04:17.324 --> 00:04:18.793 position:19% line:89% align:start
Good morning, Roberto.

00:04:18.826 --> 00:04:21.129 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry that you had to
go train with him

00:04:21.162 --> 00:04:22.864 position:16% line:89% align:start
so early in the morning.

00:04:22.897 --> 00:04:23.463 position:35% line:89% align:start
No problem.

00:04:23.497 --> 00:04:24.799 position:33% line:83% align:start
[Mrs. Ozora]
Really...

00:04:24.832 --> 00:04:26.934 position:19% line:83% align:start
When it's about soccer,
he can't see anything else.

00:04:26.968 --> 00:04:30.538 position:19% line:83% align:start
Just say no if he asks
for something impossible.

00:04:30.571 --> 00:04:32.774 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Roberto] It's okay...
It was actually me who...

00:04:32.807 --> 00:04:35.209 position:27% line:83% align:start
proposed to have
an early morning practice.

00:04:35.243 --> 00:04:37.512 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh... Is that so?

00:04:37.545 --> 00:04:38.780 position:16% line:89% align:start
I guess it's fine, but...

00:04:38.813 --> 00:04:39.781 position:44% line:89% align:start
Oh...

00:04:39.814 --> 00:04:42.784 position:19% line:83% align:start
If it's about my eyes,
you don't have to worry.

00:04:42.817 --> 00:04:43.718 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-You've seen

00:04:43.751 --> 00:04:45.920 position:24% line:83% align:start
my medical report,
haven't you?

00:04:45.953 --> 00:04:48.222 position:24% line:89% align:start
Um... I'm so sorry.

00:04:48.256 --> 00:04:49.991 position:10% line:89% align:start
I just couldn't help myself.

00:04:51.092 --> 00:04:52.459 position:35% line:83% align:start
[narrator]
 <i>Diagnosis report...</i>

00:04:52.492 --> 00:04:54.061 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Mr. Roberto Hongo.</i>

00:04:55.196 --> 00:04:57.765 position:30% line:83% align:start
The real reason
why I came here...

00:04:57.799 --> 00:04:59.700 position:21% line:83% align:start
was to be examined by
the specialist

00:04:59.734 --> 00:05:02.003 position:24% line:83% align:start
that Captain Ozora
recommended.

00:05:03.070 --> 00:05:05.372 position:27% line:83% align:start
You already know
how that turned out.

00:05:05.405 --> 00:05:07.842 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'll never be able to
return to the pitch again.

00:05:09.010 --> 00:05:12.146 position:13% line:83% align:start
I've informed my team about
my intention to retire.

00:05:12.180 --> 00:05:13.380 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh.

00:05:13.413 --> 00:05:17.084 position:21% line:83% align:start
But now, I'm actually
enjoying being a coach.

00:05:17.118 --> 00:05:21.488 position:13% line:83% align:start
Besides... I'm having a lot
of fun teaching Tsubasa.

00:05:21.522 --> 00:05:23.925 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Roberto] Yes.
He is something else...

00:05:23.958 --> 00:05:24.725 position:41% line:89% align:start
He is.

00:05:25.726 --> 00:05:27.829 position:21% line:83% align:start
The more I teach him,
the better he gets.

00:05:27.862 --> 00:05:28.796 position:19% line:89% align:start
If I keep training him,

00:05:28.830 --> 00:05:31.498 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm sure I will forget
about my condition.

00:05:32.700 --> 00:05:33.801 position:38% line:89% align:start
Roberto.

00:05:34.735 --> 00:05:37.305 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm really taking it
easy out there.

00:05:37.337 --> 00:05:38.539 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:05:39.941 --> 00:05:41.776 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Ryo]
Okay, here we go!

00:05:41.809 --> 00:05:46.914 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:05:46.948 --> 00:05:48.481 position:35% line:89% align:start
Ah! Oh! Uh!

00:05:48.516 --> 00:05:49.984 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Whoa!
-[grunting]

00:05:50.017 --> 00:05:51.886 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Oh, excuse me!

00:05:53.888 --> 00:05:56.324 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:05:56.356 --> 00:05:57.658 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scream]

00:05:58.059 --> 00:05:59.026 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sigh]

00:05:59.727 --> 00:06:03.231 position:44% line:83% align:start
Wait!
Don't go that way!

00:06:03.264 --> 00:06:05.533 position:24% line:83% align:start
Big news! Big news!
Big news!

00:06:05.566 --> 00:06:07.235 position:19% line:83% align:start
I have to tell everyone
right away.

00:06:07.268 --> 00:06:09.136 position:19% line:83% align:start
I have to tell everyone
right away!

