[grunts]

00:06:32.193 --> 00:06:35.663 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:06:36.697 --> 00:06:42.937 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:06:43.504 --> 00:06:45.339 position:33% line:89% align:start
Aw, I'm late!

00:06:45.373 --> 00:06:47.642 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:06:49.343 --> 00:06:50.811 position:35% line:83% align:start
[teacher 1]
So, let's begin our class.

00:06:50.845 --> 00:06:52.947 position:33% line:83% align:start
At the end of
last school year...

00:06:52.980 --> 00:06:54.414 position:16% line:89% align:start
I asked every one of you

00:06:54.447 --> 00:06:56.717 position:16% line:83% align:start
to pick a book they like
from the library.

00:06:58.119 --> 00:06:59.620 position:38% line:83% align:start
However,
some of you are new.

00:06:59.654 --> 00:07:00.721 position:30% line:83% align:start
- <i>I knew Manabu</i>
-[teacher 1] So I understand

00:07:00.755 --> 00:07:01.389 position:27% line:83% align:start
- <i>would be late.</i>
-if you haven't selected

00:07:01.421 --> 00:07:02.823 position:30% line:89% align:start
your book yet.

00:07:02.857 --> 00:07:04.625 position:10% line:83% align:start
- <i>He's terrible at dribbling.</i>
-This week, you still have

00:07:04.659 --> 00:07:06.961 position:16% line:83% align:start
time to go by the school
library and pick a book.

00:07:06.994 --> 00:07:08.162 position:33% line:89% align:start
Ryo! Tsubasa!

00:07:08.195 --> 00:07:09.931 position:33% line:83% align:start
I've got some
big news, guys!

00:07:09.964 --> 00:07:11.599 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:07:11.632 --> 00:07:12.667 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:07:12.700 --> 00:07:13.868 position:38% line:89% align:start
Uh-oh...

00:07:14.802 --> 00:07:15.803 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

