-How embarrassing!
-[student] [laughs]

00:07:18.706 --> 00:07:20.808 position:10% line:83% align:start
[student] Oh my God. Did you
see the game today?

00:07:20.841 --> 00:07:21.976 position:30% line:83% align:start
-It was crazy!
-Shutetsu Elementary

00:07:22.009 --> 00:07:24.578 position:19% line:83% align:start
-has a practice match?
-No doubt about it.

00:07:24.612 --> 00:07:25.880 position:24% line:83% align:start
When I walked home
yesterday,

00:07:25.913 --> 00:07:28.883 position:35% line:83% align:start
I passed by
Mizukoshi Elementary.

00:07:28.916 --> 00:07:30.651 position:27% line:83% align:start
So, the guys from
the soccer club

00:07:30.685 --> 00:07:32.586 position:13% line:89% align:start
