of town!

00:07:41.729 --> 00:07:43.030 position:19% line:89% align:start
I had no other choice.

00:07:43.064 --> 00:07:45.700 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Manabu] The ball just
didn't want to listen to me.

00:07:45.733 --> 00:07:47.467 position:19% line:89% align:start
But... Thanks to that,

00:07:47.501 --> 00:07:50.905 position:19% line:83% align:start
I was able to find out
about the practice match.

00:07:50.938 --> 00:07:51.572 position:44% line:89% align:start
Oh...

00:07:51.605 --> 00:07:53.473 position:13% line:89% align:start
Let's go watch it, Tsubasa.

00:07:53.507 --> 00:07:55.076 position:13% line:89% align:start
The tournament starts soon.

00:07:55.109 --> 00:07:56.444 position:16% line:89% align:start
We should see them play!

00:07:56.476 --> 00:07:57.745 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

