[Hanji]
Of course not!

00:08:35.016 --> 00:08:36.917 position:24% line:83% align:start
He won't be playing
in this match.

00:08:36.951 --> 00:08:37.952 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:08:37.985 --> 00:08:39.754 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[Ryo] Hanji!
-[Masato] I see now.

00:08:39.787 --> 00:08:41.822 position:16% line:83% align:start
