-Huh?!
-Well, even without Genzo,

00:08:57.705 --> 00:09:00.841 position:13% line:83% align:start
they'll easily win against
an opponent like Mizukoshi.

00:09:00.875 --> 00:09:02.777 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yaaayyyyyyy!

00:09:02.810 --> 00:09:03.878 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Masato]
It's already 3 - 0

00:09:03.911 --> 00:09:05.780 position:24% line:83% align:start
andthey're just in
the first half!

00:09:05.813 --> 00:09:08.517 position:16% line:83% align:start
Mizukoshi isn't supposed
to be such a weak team.

00:09:08.549 --> 00:09:11.886 position:27% line:83% align:start
But, Shutetsu has
a very strong team as usual.

00:09:11.919 --> 00:09:14.188 position:38% line:83% align:start
Come on!
Mizukoshi Elementary!

00:09:14.221 --> 00:09:15.656 position:24% line:89% align:start
Just do your best!

00:09:15.689 --> 00:09:17.224 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Ohhh!
-Ohhh!

00:09:19.827 --> 00:09:20.861 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:09:20.895 --> 00:09:22.830 position:35% line:83% align:start
-He got it!
-He's wide open!

