00:20:23.256 --> 00:20:24.357 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>We've progressed a lot!</i>

00:20:24.391 --> 00:20:26.293 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>And it's all thanks</i>
 <i>to you, Tsubasa!</i>

00:20:26.326 --> 00:20:28.830 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>He really inspires</i>
 <i>all of us!</i>

00:20:28.863 --> 00:20:30.932 position:38% line:89% align:start
